{"tid":1141326,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家希望咩經典系列可以再出續集","createTime":"2019-05-06T11:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T13:41:25.000Z","uid":213533,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7dceda5b2a14da82f4e0caa9d7781635d4e671","tid":1141326,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"大家咁多年應該玩過唔少驚<br />\n其中，應該有d驚應該幾好<br />\n不過可惜的是多年來已經無哂消息<br />\n唔知大家希望咩驚可以再出續作<br />\n<br />\n我自己最希望出續作的是《皇家騎士團》一款好經典的戰棋遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過e家戰棋驚都好似唔係好得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Jump Ultimate Star》，少年Jump系列我自己覺得最好玩的驚，好記得可以養成d漫畫角色做六格漫畫，然後用漫畫砌Team。不過唔知點解Bandai改左個發展方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外最近玩大亂鬥Labo VR命魂時，會出現的《零》系列如果可以配合相機VR一齊玩，個效果應該會幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起Bandai，記得以前出過一部叫WonderSwan Color 的機的數碼暴龍驚都好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（記得玩過Digimon Trainer Battle Spirit ，D-project同激鬥戰車）"},{"pid":"1d0308e332a0e6a36446173eb679e68305ab4f38","tid":1141326,"uid":20171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"大航海時代<br />\n<br />\nJet set radio<br />\n<br />\nDrag on dragoon<br />\n<br />\nSonic adventure"},{"pid":"38105db43f6023ffa36b2b2a3684202984459508","tid":1141326,"uid":26953,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score